c Website</h1>\r\n[divider height=\"40\"]\r\n\r\ncenter\r\n\r\n#252c2d\r\n\r\nno-repeat;center top;;\r\n\r\n20px\r\n\r\n10px 10px 10px\r\n\r\nzoomIn\r\n\r\nHeading + desc\r\n\r\n<h3>Kevin Wilkinson, Ex Tresu U.K</h3>\r\n\r\nno-repeat;center top;;\r\n\r\n20px\r\n\r\nDesc\r\n\r\n<h6> This site is dedicated to latest developments available for Chambered Doctor Blade Systems & Anilox Roller Technology in the UK.\r\nI offer a range of services to cater for individual needs  at competitive prices:\r\n<br />\r\nTroubleshooting on existing chamber & anilox roller systems specialist knowledge: Heidelberg, Komori, KBA, Man Roland & Mitsubishi. (Any chamber system, offset or flexo). Conversions from existing metering roll systems </h6>\r\n\r\nno-repeat;center top;;\r\n\r\n20px\r\n\r\nDesc\r\n\r\n<h5>Quality</h5>\r\n<p>  If you feel your system is past its best  and becoming inefficient. Non corrosive lightweight Stainless Steel replacement chambers can be designed for all sizes and all makes of press.\r\n<br />\r\nLight weight laser engraved ceramic anilox rollers, using the latest screen technology. Designed too give maximum efficiency with less blocking. Cell structure and line count to suite product need. </p>\r\n\r\nno-repeat;center top;;\r\n\r\nDesc\r\n\r\n<h5>Service Visits</h5>\r\n<p>Specialised Anilox Roller Cleaning Service: Onsite chemically cleaned, during a service visit.\r\nPeristaltic Circulators: fully automatic cleaning, temperature controlled. Eco-friendly roller and chamber cleaning system.\r\n</br>\r\nA complete range of Doctor Blade to suite individual needs.\r\n</br>\r\nThe new poly/steel combination is cleaning up the industry.\r\n\r\nAn alternative end seal arrangement,to fit a Tresu D2. Full range of impregnated felt seal to suite all H&B chamber systems\r\n</p>\r\n\r\nno-repeat;center top;;\r\n\r\nHeading\r\n\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n\r\nno-repeat;center top;;\r\n\r\n20px\r\n\r\nhttp://www.chambers-inc.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/PROD_TRESU-FlexiPrint-IMW-E-Line-Chamber-Doctor-Blade_7by5-3.png\r\n\r\ncenter\r\n\r\n'),(42,11,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(43,11,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(44,11,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(45,11,'_menu_item_object_id','10'),(46,11,'_menu_item_object','page'),(47,11,'_menu_item_target',''),(48,11,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(49,11,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(50,11,'_menu_item_url',''),(51,11,'menu-item-mfn-megamenu',''),(52,11,'menu-item-mfn-bg',''),(53,20,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(54,20,'_wp_page_template','default'),(55,20,'mfn-post-hide-content','0'),(56,20,'mfn-post-slider','0'),(57,20,'mfn-post-slider-layer','0'),(58,20,'mfn-post-custom-layout','0'),(59,20,'mfn-post-one-page','0'),(60,20,'mfn-post-hide-title','0'),(61,20,'mfn-post-remove-padding','1'),(62,20,'mfn-post-menu','0'),(63,20,'mfn-page-items',''),(155,49,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:576;s:6:\"height\";i:350;s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"2015/12/home_industry_map.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:8:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"home_industry_map-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"home_industry_map-300x182.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:182;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"home_industry_map-240x146.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:240;s:6:\"height\";i:146;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:5:\"50x50\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"home_industry_map-50x30.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:50;s:6:\"height\";i:30;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:14:\"clients-slider\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:28:\"home_industry_map-123x75.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:123;s:6:\"height\";i:75;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:12:\"testimonials\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"home_industry_map-85x85.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:85;s:6:\"height\";i:85;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:9:\"blog-navi\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:27:\"home_industry_map-80x80.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:80;s:6:\"height\";i:80;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:14:\"portfolio-mf-t\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:29:\"home_industry_map-480x350.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:480;s:6:\"height\";i:350;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}}s:10:\"image_meta\";a:12:{s:8:\"aperture\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"credit\";s:0:\"\";s:6:\"camera\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"caption\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:1:\"0\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"0\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:0:{}}}'),(64,20,'mfn-page-items-seo','Heading\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #fff;\">Copper pipes</h2>\n[divider height=\"30\"]\n<p style=\"color: #fff;\">Cras eleifend lorem tincidunt scelerisque sollicitudin. Nulla efficitur urna sit amet enim tempor pellentesque eleifend lorem.</p>\n[divider height=\"30\"]\n[button title=\"Read more\" link=\"http://themes.muffingroup.com/be/industry/product-details/\" color=\"#0c1314\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" large=\"1\"]\n\ncenter\n\nrgba(167, 123, 108, 0.9)\n\n40px 20px 30px\n\nHeading\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #fff;\">Aluminum pipes</h2>\n[divider height=\"30\"]\n<p style=\"color: #fff;\">Sed finibus, massa tempor condimentum mollis, tortor eros ultricies quam, eget eleifend diam ipsum at quam. Aenean urna orci ullamcorpe.</p>\n[divider height=\"30\"]\n[button title=\"Read more\" link=\"http://themes.muffingroup.com/be/industry/product-details/\" color=\"#0c1314\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" large=\"1\"]\n\ncenter\n\nrgba(151, 158, 160, 0.9)\n\n40px 20px 30px\n\nHeading\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #fff;\">PVC pipes</h2>\n[divider height=\"30\"]\n<p style=\"color: #fff;\">Praesent massa massa, cursus nec nulla non, vestibulum laoreet ligula. Fusce commodo orci a arcu consectetur lobortis. Praesent blandit odio arcu viverra fusce.</p>\n[divider height=\"30\"]\n[button title=\"Read more\" link=\"http://themes.muffingroup.com/be/industry/product-details/\" color=\"#0c1314\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" large=\"1\"]\n\ncenter\n\nrgba(166, 166, 166, 0.9)\n\n40px 20px 30px\n\n'),(65,22,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(66,22,'_wp_page_template','default'),(67,22,'mfn-post-hide-content','0'),(68,22,'mfn-post-slider','0'),(69,22,'mfn-post-slider-layer','0'),(70,22,'mfn-post-custom-layout','0'),(71,22,'mfn-post-one-page','0'),(72,22,'mfn-post-hide-title','0'),(73,22,'mfn-post-remove-padding','1'),(74,22,'mfn-post-menu','0'),(75,22,'mfn-page-items',''),(76,22,'mfn-page-items-seo','Heading + desc\n\n<h3>The Company</h3>\r\n[divider height=\"20\"]\r\n<h5></h5>\r\n[divider height=\"20\"]\r\n<p class=\"big\">\r\nNew Company - Familiar Face.\r\nIf you have installed a new press or had your original system converted, successfully, in the last 10 years with a chambered doctor blade system; it was probably me! During this time, I maintained the interests of the Tresu Group in the U.K. in a period when, the expectations of the chamber system changed dramatically. It has now become an integral part of the high speed, high volume manufacturing process. Quick turn round, fully protected and enhanced on all substrates and that is just the basics. \r\nMy background is in engineering. I am an apprentice trained millwright, capable of manufacturing parts and installing them, working to very strict tolerances.\r\nI first came into contact with paper and print when I assembled and installed Unwind/Rewind Auto splice unit for offset webs, moving into high speed die-cutting and Flexo-graphic print in corrugated and now Chambered Doctor Blade systems predominantly in offset for Heidelberg, Komori, KBA, Mitsubishi and Roland Litho-presses. More recently chamber systems in Flexo, on F&K, Sciavi and Gopfert systems.\r\n<br />\r\n</p>\n\njustify\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\n20px 0 0 0\n\nhttp://www.chambers-inc.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Kev.jpg\n\n600\n\ncenter\n\n50\n\nzoomIn\n\n30\n\ndefault\n\nhttp://www.chambers-inc.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/installDSCF0080.jpg\n\ncenter\n\nzoomInDown\n\nDesc\n\n[divider height=\"20\"]\r\n<p class=\"big\">\r\nI quickly found out, even if I was the best engineer in the world, to make a chamber system work to its potential I had to become an applications engineer and a chemist. I had to know the reaction of paper, card and plastics to all variations of varnishes and because I concentrated purely on the coating unit I discovered problems a normal print demonstrator may only see once in a lifetime.\r\n</p>\n\njustify\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\n50px 0 0 7%\n\nHeading + desc\n\n<h4>Why use Chambers Inc?</h4>\r\n[divider height=\"30\"]\r\n<p class=\"big\">Don\'t lose control of your roller, cleaning on-site will guarantee safe handling and avoid unexpected surprises. .</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nHeading + desc\n\n<h3></h3>\r\n[divider height=\"30\"]\r\n<p class=\"big\"> The steel/poly combination reduces downtime and wasted time cleaning the chamber. Reverse Doctoring is a thing of the past.\r\n<br />\r\nComplete satisfaction with this product guaranteed </p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nHeading + desc\n\n<h3></h3>\r\n[divider height=\"30\"]\r\n<p class=\"big\">I have worked with every varnish range, anilox supplier and every type of transfer blanket and polymer plate. No two customers are alike.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\n'),(78,24,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(79,24,'_wp_page_template','default'),(80,24,'mfn-post-hide-content','0'),(81,24,'mfn-post-slider','0'),(82,24,'mfn-post-slider-layer','0'),(83,24,'mfn-post-custom-layout','0'),(84,24,'mfn-post-one-page','0'),(85,24,'mfn-post-hide-title','0'),(86,24,'mfn-post-remove-padding','1'),(87,24,'mfn-post-menu','0'),(88,24,'mfn-page-items',''),(89,24,'mfn-page-items-seo','Address\n\n<h3>Address</h3>\r\n<p>Snail Mail adress is:</br> Chambers Inc Ltd, 20 Boyds Walk, Dukinfield. SK16 4TW. </p>\r\n[divider height=\"30\"]\r\n<div style=\"padding-left: 65px; background: url(http://www.chambers-inc.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/home_industry_pin2.png) no-repeat left top;\">\r\n<h6>CALL US NOW</h6>\r\n<p>The fastest way to get a response is to call on this number</p>\r\n<p>Call us +44 (0) 7849 755 038<br />\r\nMail: <a href=\"#\">info@chambers-inc.co.uk</a></p>\r\n</div>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nContact form\n\n<h3>Email us</h3>\r\n<p class=\"big\">Please use this form to get in touch, Provide us with as much information about your enquiry as possible. \r\nWe aim to reply to all emails within 24/48 hours, excluding weekends and Bank Holidays.</p>\r\n[divider height=\"20\"]\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"4\" title=\"Contact form 1\"]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nHeading\n\n<h3> Please Note:</h3>\r\n<p class=\"big\">We will do our our best to get back in touch within 24 hours, but sometimes we may not get back immediately. If you need us fast then please call the phone number above. </br>\r\nThank you</br>\r\nKev Wilkinson</br>\r\nM.D.</br>\r\n(A.K.A. The Chamber Doctor)\r\n</p>\n\nleft\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\n0 10% 0 0\n\n'),(495,110,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1600;s:6:\"height\";i:1200;s:4:\"file\";s:44:\"2015/12/Chambers-Inc-Contact-Us-DSCF0074.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:16:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:44:\"Chambers-Inc-Contact-Us-DSCF0074-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:44:\"Chambers-Inc-Contact-Us-DSCF0074-300x225.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:225;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:44:\"Chambers-Inc-Contact-Us-DSCF0074-768x576.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:576;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:45:\"Chambers-Inc-Contact-Us-DSCF0074-1024x768.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:768;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:44:\"Chambers-Inc-Contact