nilox roller systems specialist knowledge: Heidelberg, Komori, KBA, Man Roland & Mitsubishi. (Any chamber system, offset or flexo). Conversions from existing metering roll systems .</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nHeading\n\n<h3 class=\"themecolor\">Working on Chamber Systems since 1999</h3>\r\n<p class=\"big\">I have worked on Chamber systems for TetraPak, Heidelberg UK, Komori UK and many more Lithographic and Flexo printers. I am confident that I can retrofit to any system.</p>\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n0 10%\n\n<img src=\"http://www.chambers-inc.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_9068.jpg\" alt=\"Chamber\"/>\n\n588\n\ncenter\n\n<img src=\"http://www.chambers-inc.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Nova_Robust_web.jpg\" alt=\"Nova_Robust_web\"/>\n\n588\n\ncenter\n\n<img src=\"http://www.chambers-inc.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Doctor_blade_rolls_header_web.jpg\" alt=\"Doctor_blade_rolls_header_web\"/>\n\n1200\n\n<img src=\"http://www.chambers-inc.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Chamber-CAD.png\" alt=\"Chamber CAD\"/>\n\n'),(501,112,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1200;s:6:\"height\";i:301;s:4:\"file\";s:41:\"2015/12/Doctor_blade_rolls_header_web.jpg\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:14:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:41:\"Doctor_blade_rolls_header_web-150x150.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:40:\"Doctor_blade_rolls_header_web-300x75.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:75;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:41:\"Doctor_blade_rolls_header_web-768x193.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:193;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:42:\"Doctor_blade_rolls_header_web-1024x257.jpg\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:257;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";}s:14:\"post-thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:40:\"Doctor_blade_rolls_header_web-260x65.jpg\"